'''俄克拉荷馬州立大學靜水校區'''（{{lang-en|Oklahoma State University-Stillwater}}，簡稱'''Oklahoma State'''、'''OK-State'''或'''OSU'''）是一所四年制公立大学，位于[[俄克拉荷馬州|俄克拉荷馬州]][[斯蒂尔沃特_(俄克拉何马州)|斯蒂尔沃特]]，是俄克拉荷马州立大学系统的主校区。该校是男女同校的[[赠地大学|赠地大学]]。

该校於1890年成立由[[土地拨赠法案|土地拨赠法案]]成立，前身属俄克拉荷马农业及机械学院（Oklahoma Agricultural and Mechanical College)。2012年秋季学期，该校注册人数为25,544人（包括静水校区和塔尔萨校区），当年新生人数为4,298人<ref>[https://news.okstate.edu/articles/final-enrollment-numbers] {{Wayback|url=https://news.okstate.edu/articles/final-enrollment-numbers |date=20150923055928 }}Final Enrollment numbers | News and Information</ref>。该校被卡内基教学促进基金会([[:en:Carnegie_Foundation_for_the_Advancement_of_Teaching|Carnegie Foundation for the Advancement of Teaching]])列为高研究活动的研究性大学<ref>{{cite web|url=http://classifications.carnegiefoundation.org/lookup_listings/view_institution.php?unit_id=207388&start_page=institution.php&clq={%22ipug2005_ids%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ipgrad2005_ids%22%3A%22%22%2C%22enrprofile2005_ids%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ugprfile2005_ids%22%3A%22%22%2C%22sizeset2005_ids%22%3A%22%22%2C%22basic2005_ids%22%3A%22%22%2C%22eng2005_ids%22%3A%22%22%2C%22search_string%22%3A%22oklahoma+state%22%2C%22level%22%3A%22%22%2C%22control%22%3A%22%22%2C%22accred%22%3A%22%22%2C%22state%22%3A%22%22%2C%22region%22%3A%22%22%2C%22urbanicity%22%3A%22%22%2C%22womens%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hbcu%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hsi%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tribal%22%3A%22%22%2C%22msi%22%3A%22%22%2C%22landgrant%22%3A%22%22%2C%22coplac%22%3A%22%22%2C%22urban%22%3A%22%22} |title=Carnegie Foundation – Oklahoma State University – Main Campus |publisher=Carnegiefoundation.org |year=2010 |accessdate=2011-09-05}}</ref>。

2011年，俄克拉何马州立大学被[[普林斯顿评论|普林斯顿评论]]评为120所“西部最佳大学”之一。2010年，被评为50所“最有价值公立大学”之一。俄克拉何马州立大学的退伍军人项目是全美最受赞誉的之一<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.princetonreview.com/schools/college/CollegeRankings.aspx?iid=1022745 |title=Princeton Review – Rankings & Lists |publisher=Princetonreview.com |date= |accessdate=February 24, 2011 |archive-date=2015-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150116035235/http://www.princetonreview.com/schools/college/CollegeRankings.aspx?iid=1022745 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年，该校在[[美国新闻与世界报道|美国新闻与世界报]]评选的“最佳公立大学”中排名第66位，在所有美国大学的排名中名列132位<ref>{{cite web |url=http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-colleges/national-top-public |title=U.S. News & World Report, Best Colleges: Top Public Schools: National Universities |publisher=Colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com |date= |accessdate=February 24, 2011 |archive-date=2009-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090826121616/http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-colleges/national-top-public |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年，该校被[[福布斯|福布斯]]评为“最有价值大学”的第23位<ref>{{cite web |url=https://news.okstate.edu/on-campus-archives/2257-forbes-names-osu-a-top-25-best-value-college |title=Forbes names OSU a top-25 Best Value College |accessdate=August 7, 2013 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140320040224/https://news.okstate.edu/on-campus-archives/2257-forbes-names-osu-a-top-25-best-value-college |archivedate=2014年3月20日 }}</ref>。

